  <title>Detection of Xanthomonas campestris mutants with increased xanthan production</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=9e57cf4afae861961032bd27b573f686&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
  <authors>
